  VERSION="4.02"
 CATEGORY="graphic security"
ATTRIBUTE="gnome|x11"
      URL="http://www.jwz.org/xscreensaver"
      REQ="glut bc zlib"
   OPT[0]="audiofile:::for audio support"
   OPT[1]="esound:::for esd audio output"
   OPT[2]="gnome-core:::for gnome support"
    SHORT="xscreensaver is a modular screen saver and locker for X Windows."
cat << EOF
XScreenSaver is a modular screen saver and locker for the X Window
System. It is highly customizable and allows the use of any program that
can draw on the root window as a display mode. More than 120 display
modes are included in this package.
EOF
